        <h2 class="collectionDesign__subtitle subtitle">Design Process</h2>
        <p class="collectionDesign__core core">Our design process for this collection was inspired by the ruggedness of the Belgian Ardennes. We embraced rough edges and exaggerated lines, a style that extends to our typography as well.</p>
        <p class="collectionDesign__core core">To achieve this effect for our ducks, we used thresholding to reduce the images to their essential outlines. Staying true to the collection’s aesthetic, we then traced over the designs by hand, amplifying the details to enhance their raw, expressive character.
        <br><br>
        This approach allows us to capture the essence of the Ardennes—untamed, textured, and deeply immersive. Every element, from the graphics to the garments themselves, reflects the raw beauty of the landscape that inspired them.</p>
